<template>
  <NoteView :note="this.note"></NoteView>
</template>

<script>
import NoteView from "./NoteView.vue"

export default {
  name: 'NoteView',
  props: {
    note: Object,
  },
  components: {
    NoteView,
  },
  data() {
    return {
      notes: [
        {
          timestamp: "12:34",
          contents: "Hello World",
        },
      ],
    }
  }
}
</script>

<style>
</style>
